ComicInfo.Title: Artificial Intelligence Part 3
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Artificial Intelligence Part 3: While Alpha-001 continues placing the Iron Grenadiers under its control, Zartan summons Crystal Ball to a meeting with the Dreadnoks. Elsewhere, the retired Oktober Guard get wind of Cobra's latest plot and decide to get involved. Snake Eyes and Scarlett stop terrorists from destroying the Statue of Liberty, while Cobra Commander plots to brainwash Snake Eyes.
